OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be largely cloudy
OL,6,Fthroughout the day with rain at times.
OL,7,FThe rain will be mainly light but a
OL,8,Ffew isolated heavy showers may develop
OL,9,Ffrom late afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FCloud and outbreaks of rain
OL,12,Fpush east in the evening, turning
OL,13,Fheavier for a time. Becoming dry for a
OL,14,Ftime, before further cloud and rain
OL,15,Farrive in the west overnight.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSunday:FCloudy and breezy throughout
OL,18,Fthe day as outbreaks of rain move
OL,19,Feast, these heavy at times. Some drier
OL,20,Fand brighter spells in the west later
OL,21,Fas the rain clears away.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
